{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                                             // hydrogen // schema // audio"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Audio pillar (Pillar 10b) - synthesis, processing, and analysis."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Leader module that re-exports all audio sub-modules."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Sub-modules"},{"LineComment":" | - **Level**: Amplitude atoms (Decibel, LinearGain, dBFS)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Frequency**: Pitch atoms (Hertz, MidiNote, Cent, Semitone, Octave)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Time**: Temporal atoms (BeatTime, BarTime, SampleCount)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Spatial**: Stereo/3D positioning (Pan, Balance, Azimuth, Elevation)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Synthesis**: Filter/oscillator params (Cutoff, Resonance, Drive)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Envelope**: ADSR atoms (Attack, Decay, Sustain, Release)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Modulation**: LFO params (ModDepth, ModRate, LFOPhase)"},{"LineComment":" | - **Analysis**: Metering atoms (RMS, Peak, FFT)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Design Philosophy"},{"LineComment":" | Audio primitives model synthesis concepts, not Web Audio API methods."},{"LineComment":" | Conversion to Web Audio, MIDI, or other backends happens at boundaries."},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Ableton-style Workflow"},{"LineComment":" | These primitives support:"},{"LineComment":" | - Clip-based arrangement with BeatTime/BarTime"},{"LineComment":" | - Synthesis with Oscillator, Filter, Envelope"},{"LineComment":" | - Effects chains with Mix, Feedback, DecayTime"},{"LineComment":" | - Real-time analysis with RMS, Peak, FFT"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Usage"},{"LineComment":" | ```purescript"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Audio.Level as Level"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Audio.Frequency as Freq"},{"LineComment":" | import Hydrogen.Schema.Audio.Envelope as Env"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Define an envelope"},{"LineComment":" | ampEnv = Env.adsr"},{"LineComment":" |   (Env.attackTime 0.01)"},{"LineComment":" |   (Env.decayTime 0.2)"},{"LineComment":" |   (Env.sustainLevel 0.7)"},{"LineComment":" |   (Env.releaseTime 0.5)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | -- Define a note"},{"LineComment":" | note = Freq.midiNote 60  -- Middle C"},{"LineComment":" | freq = Freq.midiToHertz note  -- 261.63 Hz"},{"LineComment":" | ```"}],"decls":[],"exports":[],"foreign":[],"imports":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[48,35],"start":[48,1]}},"moduleName":["Prim"]}],"moduleName":["Hydrogen","Schema","Audio"],"modulePath":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Audio.purs","reExports":{},"sourceSpan":{"end":[48,35],"start":[48,1]}}